### Describe the bug

During error handling in  KeycloakErrorHandler, there are situations where the JEE context is no longer active. 
This could lead to a follow-up exception hiding the original exception. 

### Version

26.4.x

### Expected behavior

Handle a missing context gracefully. 

### Actual behavior

Throwing an exception that is most likely hiding the original exception and error handling.

